snippet.title: RESIDENT EVIL Gamecube REMAKE – Chris Redfield FULL GAME Walkthrough - ALL ENDINGS 100% Collectibles
snippet.description:
Welcome to this new walkthrough series, featuring the original Gamecube remake of the horror classic “Resident Evil”.
This Chris Redfield walkthrough guide features all the four possible endings, achieving a 100% lore recollection of the saga's first entry.
Enjoy :)
